通例</strong>，但如果成隊人都係軍裝你就吹佢唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：非法律撚，要保護好自己就要了解呢啲條例<br />\n警察通例 第20章 警署與各科組日常處理的事務：<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo020.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpgo%2Ftc%2FCpgo020.pdf&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=126856a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo020.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"2b758f72c18cc2a672e62333bd081af49aece39d","tid":1219912,"uid":162331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b9c07285de0590d98c02670daef4db60c562c67","tid":1219912,"uid":213533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:09:03.000Z","msg":"情景題：<br />\n一班警察<br />\n如果有一部份人有委任證<br />\n一部份人無委任證<br />\n<br />\n有委任證的不停的保著另外無委任證的<br />\n<br />\n可以點做？我們其實是不是可以要求有委任證的立即拘捕無委任證的？<br />\n承上，如果有委任證的拒絕，是不是有法律責任？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題目二：<br />\n委任證的真偽點分？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:59:59.000Z","msg":"第二題有人講過<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1204624/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1204624/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">不過偉大祖國最叻造山寨貨，check 咗都唔知有冇用</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過香港市民既然有權去check就梗係<strong>慢慢</strong>睇清楚"},{"pid":"0f880829a43839fdc4f273ba938978b5d29cb525","tid":1219912,"uid":213533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"有沒有人可以解一解題一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/